title: Dawn Complete [h33t] [Alieneye]
description:
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dawn_(comics)" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dawn_(comics)</a> 

Dawn is character that appears in various books written and drawn by Joeseph Micheal Linsner. Linsner has garnered some acclaim by farming out his talents as a cover artist with varying degrees of success and quality over the years.  However, whenever he returns to working on a Dawn project, the quality of his work is unsurpassed. The books themselves are a heady mix of horror, occult, action, and sex. Altogether, fun and reliable reads. Enjoy.
